- Lil, grab my hand. - Come on, Noah.

868
01:02:22,060 --> 01:02:23,230
莉莉 你没事吧?
Lilly, you okay?

869
01:02:23,730 --> 01:02:27,570
罗斯韦尔和玛丽莲・梦露 地图 地图!
Roswell and Marilyn Monroe, maps, maps.

870
01:02:27,610 --> 01:02:31,530
- 都上来了吗? - 杰克逊!
- Everybody on? Ready? - Jackson!

871
01:02:33,850 --> 01:02:35,780
他在哪儿? 他在干嘛?
Where is he? What's he doing?

872
01:02:49,610 --> 01:02:52,550
- 爹地 - 不要
- Daddy! - No!

873
01:02:56,450 --> 01:02:58,020
凯特 我们必须走了
Kate. We have to go.

874
01:02:58,060 --> 01:02:59,440
不 我们哪儿也不去!
No, we're not going anywhere!

875
01:02:59,470 --> 01:03:00,730
孩子们 系好安全带 我们要起飞了
Kids, buckle up. We're leaving.

876
01:03:00,760 --> 01:03:03,770
他是我爸爸 我们得等他!
He's my dad. We're gonna wait!

877
01:03:08,320 --> 01:03:09,820
不
No!

878
01:03:10,110 --> 01:03:12,360
爹地
Daddy!

879
01:03:15,450 --> 01:03:20,120
等等 戈登 我看见他了
Wait! Wait. Gordon, I see something.

880
01:03:24,460 --> 01:03:27,250
是爹地
It's Daddy!

881
01:03:30,130 --> 01:03:31,880
减速
Slow down!

882
01:03:31,920 --> 01:03:33,630
杰克逊 快点!
Jackson, come on!

883
01:03:34,220 --> 01:03:37,430
杰克逊 抓住我的手
Jackson. Reach for my hand!

884
01:03:37,460 --> 01:03:38,680
快点!
Grab!

885
01:03:39,310 --> 01:03:40,730
快到跑道尽头了
We're running out of runway.

886
01:03:40,770 --> 01:03:42,700
凯特 快拉他上来
For God's sakes, Kate, pull him up.

887
01:03:42,770 --> 01:03:45,690
杰克逊 抓住我的手
Jackson. Reach for my hand!

888
01:03:52,040 --> 01:03:54,570
行了 我们起飞
Right. Here we go!

889
01:03:55,690 --> 01:03:57,910
快点 再快点
Come on! Faster. Faster.

890
01:04:17,060 --> 01:04:18,550
坐好了
Hang on

891
01:04:21,080 --> 01:04:24,230
- 再快点! - 我在尽力!
- Go faster! - I'm trying!

892
01:04:39,980 --> 01:04:44,740
好了 我们安全了 安全了
Okay. We're good. We're good.

893
01:04:48,410 --> 01:04:52,540
那么 地图拿到了 我们现在要去哪儿?
So. Now that you got your map, where are we going?

894
01:04:58,170 --> 01:05:00,380
中国

895
01:05:02,880 --> 01:05:05,000
我们得找架大飞机
We're gonna need a bigger plane.

896
01:05:12,310 --> 01:05:15,190
妈妈 你刚才说了 你说过了
You know you just said that, Mom. You just said that.

897
01:05:15,230 --> 01:05:17,350
你不记得你刚说过吗?
You don't remember that you just said that?

898
01:05:17,390 --> 01:05:20,450
没事 没事
That's okay. That's okay.

899
01:05:20,480 --> 01:05:25,150
妈妈 下周我再给你打电话 还是这个时间
Listen, Mom. I'll call you next week, same time.

900
01:05:25,200 --> 01:05:29,500
好吗? 注意身体 好好照顾自己
Okay? Take care now. Take care of yourself.

901
01:05:32,490 --> 01:05:36,800
长官 我想你有必要看看这个
Sir. I think you need to see this.

902
01:05:42,090 --> 01:05:45,130
长官 我以为他们给你多留了一张票
I thought they'd give you an extra ticket, Sir.

903
01:05:45,170 --> 01:05:46,130
是给了
They did.

904
01:05:46,430 --> 01:05:50,300
可我妈妈已经89岁高龄 还坐着轮椅
But my mother is almost 89. She's in a wheelchair.

905
01:05:50,360 --> 01:05:52,200
脑子也不清醒
And she is easily confused.

906
01:05:52,250 --> 01:05:55,850
但我确信 她想以自己的方式去见创造她的上帝
And I am confident that she'll want to meet her maker on her own terms.

907
01:05:55,900 --> 01:05:58,010
- 明白吗? - 是 长官
- Okay? - Yes, sir.

908
01:05:58,600 --> 01:06:00,190
- 那你带谁走? - 谁也不带!
- Who are you bringing? - Nobody.

909
01:06:00,980 --> 01:06:04,150
我前妻跟我说 再也不想见到我
My ex-wife said she never wanted to see me again.

910
01:06:04,190 --> 01:06:05,280
那就别见
So be it.

911
01:06:05,320 --> 01:06:07,530
我们要带有用的人
We could bring people that contribute.

912
01:06:08,740 --> 01:06:11,490
南美洲已被一系列大地震所摧毁
South Africa continent has been damaged by a series of major earthquakes.

913
01:06:11,530 --> 01:06:15,020
死亡人数超过200万
The death toll is expected to be well over 2 million people.

914
01:06:15,050 --> 01:06:18,500
里约热内卢的景象更是惨不忍睹
The devastation in Rio de Janeiro is beyond imagination.

915
01:06:18,540 --> 01:06:24,170
两次8.5级地震使人们涌上街头疯抢食物
Two 8.5 tremors have left the people in the street fighting for resources.

916
01:06:24,210 --> 01:06:28,510
一小时前我们收到巴西新闻台的画面
In the last hour we received this video from Globo News, Brazil.

917
01:06:29,050 --> 01:06:31,800
怎么了? 天啊!

918
01:06:31,850 --> 01:06:35,310
基督像倒塌了!

919
01:06:35,350 --> 01:06:37,560
恐惧和骚乱弥漫全球
Fear and chaos have spread throughout the globe.

920
01:06:37,600 --> 01:06:41,440
在伦敦 第30届奥运会已经停止
As in London, where the 30th Olympic Games has been suspended.

921
01:06:41,470 --> 01:06:43,940
成千上万的群众朝唐宁街方向示威游行
Hundreds of thousands are marching towards 10 Downing Street

922
01:06:43,980 --> 01:06:47,490
要求首相解除信息封锁
demanding a lift of the information blackout proposed by the Prime Minister.

923
01:06:47,530 --> 01:06:50,030
上千个电话打进来 我们不得不关闭电话系统
Thousands of calls to the switchboard. We had to shut it down.

924
01:06:50,070 --> 01:06:52,780
我们接到全球各地的报告
We're receiving reports from all across the globe.

925
01:06:52,910 --> 01:06:57,370
无数恐慌的民众聚集在各地的公共场所
Millions of distraught masses are gathering in public places everywhere,

926
01:06:57,410 --> 01:06:58,880
绝望的向上天祈祷
converging in desperate prayer.

927
01:06:58,910 --> 01:07:02,330
各种宗教的传教士走上美国的大街小巷
Preachers of many faiths have taken their message of

928
01:07:02,370 --> 01:07:04,920
宣称世界即将灭亡
the end of the world to the streets all over the U.S.

929
01:07:04,960 --> 01:07:07,260
忏悔吧 时间不多了
Repent. There is still time.

930
01:07:07,300 --> 01:07:09,470
那些举标志牌的人
Kind of gaulling when you realize the nutbags

931
01:07:09,510 --> 01:07:11,680
原来一直是对的 真讽刺啊
with the cardboard signs had it right the whole time.

932
01:07:11,710 --> 01:07:13,740
说到外面的民众 长官
All these people out there, sir.

933
01:07:13,770 --> 01:07:15,730
我们现在还不发布警告吗?
Shouldn't we be issuing warnings now?

934
01:07:15,760 --> 01:07:18,060
只能等登船程序结束后再说
Only when the boarding process is complete.

935
01:07:18,090 --> 01:07:18,900
这是计划
That's the plan.

936
01:07:18,930 --> 01:07:20,800
2010年加拿大峰会定的 记得吗?
British Columbia 2010, remember?

937
01:07:20,840 --> 01:07:23,900
长官? 长官 那些计划是两年前制定的
Sir? Sir, those plans were drawn up 2 years ago.

938
01:07:24,060 --> 01:07:26,740
好 大家先出去 快点 先出去
Okay, everybody out. Come on, get out.

939
01:07:30,070 --> 01:07:32,000
峰会不是也确定了人类有权
Wasn't it also decided that people have the right to

940
01:07:32,040 --> 01:07:34,040
为了生存而斗争吗?
fight for their lives, best way they can?

941
01:07:34,090 --> 01:07:36,990
那也得等所有人上船了再说 艾德里安
After we get everyone on board, Adrian.

942
01:07:37,030 --> 01:07:38,370
我认为这是错误的
I think that's wrong.

943
01:07:39,330 --> 01:07:42,200
告诉人们他们死定了?
Want to tell everyone they're doomed?

944
01:07:42,300 --> 01:07:43,600
会引发暴乱的
There'd be anarchy.

945
01:07:43,950 --> 01:07:46,550
- 你想让总统被困在这里吗? - 继续说
- You want to jeopardize the departure of the president? - Come on

946
01:07:46,580 --> 01:07:51,220
我们的使命是确保人类的延续
Our mission is to assure the continuity of our species.

947
01:07:52,260 --> 01:07:55,640
我的疑问是 我能指望你吗?
My question: Can I count on you?

948
01:07:55,680 --> 01:07:56,930
能吗?
Can I?

949
01:07:57,970 --> 01:07:59,190
什么事?
What?

950
01:07:59,220 --> 01:08:01,230
黄石公园火山爆发了 长官
The Yellowstone Caldera has erupted, sir.

951
01:08:01,270 --> 01:08:04,060
火山灰将在7小时后到达华盛顿
The ash cloud will reach Washington in 7 hours.

952
01:08:05,440 --> 01:08:07,230
我们得赶快让总统上飞机
We've to get the president on board.

953
01:08:08,610 --> 01:08:09,800
总统在哪儿 萨莉?
Where is the president, Sally?

954
01:08:09,840 --> 01:08:11,700
他说想一个人静一静
Said he wanted to spend some time alone.

955
01:08:11,740 --> 01:08:14,660
- 我觉得他在小教堂里 - 他现在还去教堂?
- I think he's at the chapel. - He's going to church now?

956
01:08:14,700 --> 01:08:18,700
他正在祷告 长官 现在除了祈祷还能干什么
He's praying, sir. Which is not such a bad idea.

957
01:08:22,080 --> 01:08:26,420
总统先生 请您立刻上空军一号
Mr. President. I need to get you on Air Force One immediately.

958
01:08:28,710 --> 01:08:30,010
让我和艾德里安单独待一会
Give me a moment with Adrian.

959
01:08:30,050 --> 01:08:32,340
不是冒犯 但我们确实没时间了
No disrespect sir, we do not have time.

960
01:08:32,380 --> 01:08:33,900
挤出时间
Make time.

961
01:08:46,230 --> 01:08:49,220
你见过我太太桃乐西吗?
Did you ever meet my wife: Dorothy?

962
01:08:49,480 --> 01:08:52,500
没有 总统先生 我没有这福气
No, sir, I never had that honor.

963
01:08:53,530 --> 01:08:56,450
她去世前一会清醒 一会昏迷
She was in and out towards the end.

964
01:08:57,480 --> 01:09:01,500
就在她去世前 她拉着我的手说
The night before she passed on, she took my hand and told me:

965
01:09:01,620 --> 01:09:05,170
"我觉得你该去抽奖"
"I think you should have a lottery"

966
01:09:06,210 --> 01:09:09,300
"每个人都该有中奖的机会"
"Everyone should have a chance to go"

967
01:09:12,420 --> 01:09:14,980
也许我们早该这么做
Maybe that's what we should have done.

968
01:09:17,550 --> 01:09:22,130
我将是美利坚合众国的最后一位总统
I'll be the last president of the United States of America.

969
01:09:22,770 --> 01:09:24,800
你知道这是什么感觉吗 孩子?
Do you know how that feels, son?

970
01:09:25,940 --> 01:09:28,500
没人能够拯救美国 总统先生
No one could have saved the country, sir.

971
01:09:30,270 --> 01:09:34,200
但我想 人民有权知道真相
And I think, I think people have a right to know.

972
01:09:35,650 --> 01:09:38,000
别担心 我会处理的
Don't worry, I'll take care of that.

973
01:09:39,910 --> 01:09:41,000
你快走吧
Go on now.

974
01:09:43,250 --> 01:09:45,000
我不会丢下您的 总统先生
Not without you, sir.

975
01:09:47,420 --> 01:09:49,000
快上飞机吧 孩子
Get on that plane, son.

976
01:09:49,670 --> 01:09:53,000
你要去的是个崭新的世界
It's a brave new world you head into.

977
01:09:53,210 --> 01:09:58,700
一个年轻的科学家抵得上20个老政客
And a young scientist will be worth 20 old politicians.

978
01:10:09,610 --> 01:10:13,360
米卡兰国际机场
拉斯维加斯

979
01:10:16,820 --> 01:10:19,200
我们应该去落基山接我父母
We should go to my parents house in the Rockies.

980
01:10:19,240 --> 01:10:22,240
这不会是你要写的疯狂故事吧 杰克逊?
This isn't one of your crazy stories, now. Right, Jackson?

981
01:10:22,280 --> 01:10:23,540
我们怎么去得了中国?
How the hell are we going to make it to China?

982
01:10:23,570 --> 01:10:24,590
嘿 戈登
Hey, Gordon.

983
01:10:24,620 --> 01:10:26,910
没有杰克逊 我们连加州都逃不出来
Without Jackson we wouldn't have made it out of California.

984
01:10:26,960 --> 01:10:28,000
诺亚 别插嘴
Noah, please.

985
01:10:36,880 --> 01:10:38,850
小心 别弄坏起落架
Be careful with the landing gear!

986
01:10:38,880 --> 01:10:41,140
别紧张 我知道自己在做什么
Easy gringo, I know what I'm doing.

987
01:10:41,170 --> 01:10:44,000
大家注意 国民警卫队刚刚通知我们
Attention! The National Guard has informed us that

988
01:10:44,050 --> 01:10:47,520
一团极度危险的火山灰 正往拉斯维加斯飘来
an extremely hazardous ash cloud is headed for the city of Las Vegas.

989
01:10:47,550 --> 01:10:49,000
你要去哪儿?
Where are you going?

990
01:10:49,350 --> 01:10:51,150
请全体人员进入室内

991
01:10:51,480 --> 01:10:52,910
快走 你不能待在这里
Move! You can't stay here.

992
01:10:52,940 --> 01:10:55,530
- 我的飞机在这里 - 这里不安全
- I have a plane here. - It's not safe.

993
01:11:06,250 --> 01:11:08,920
这消息你确认过了吗?
So you got positive confirmation on this?

994
01:11:10,210 --> 01:11:12,250
谢谢你 我了解了
Thank you, I understand.

995
01:11:22,680 --> 01:11:24,810
总统先生不来了
The President is not coming.

996
01:11:29,640 --> 01:11:35,350
听着 船长不愿舍弃他下沉的的船
So, the Captain doesn't want to abandon his sinking ship.

997
01:11:35,900 --> 01:11:39,000
那是他的抉择 高尚的抉择
That's his choice, and a noble one.

998
01:11:39,480 --> 01:11:43,240
我也刚收到消息 副总统的直升机
I have also just learned that the Vice President's chopper

999
01:11:43,570 --> 01:11:46,900
在匹兹堡外的火山灰中坠毁了
went down in the ash cloud outside Pittsburgh.

1000
01:11:47,370 --> 01:11:51,370
幸运的是 我们还有宪法可循
Fortunately, we have protocols to follow.

1001
01:11:51,420 --> 01:11:52,800
那众议院议长呢?
What about the Speaker of the House?

1002
01:11:52,830 --> 01:11:54,740
这么混乱 我哪知道他在哪儿?
In this chaos, I have no idea. Where is he?

1003
01:11:54,780 --> 01:11:55,850
现在他应该是总指挥 长官
He's the Commander in Chief now, sir.

1004
01:11:55,900 --> 01:11:59,520
谁让他迟到了 这趟飞机不等人的
I don't know what to tell you. This is one flight he shouldn't be late for.

1005
01:11:59,970 --> 01:12:01,270
告诉机长 准备起飞
Tell the Captain we're taking off.

1006
01:12:01,300 --> 01:12:03,000
长官 你没有这个权力
Sir, you don't have the authority.

1007
01:12:03,180 --> 01:12:05,470
谁有这个权利? 你吗?
Who got the authority? You? You got the authority?

1008
01:12:05,510 --> 01:12:07,400
你连自己的嘴都管不住
You couldn't even keep your damn mouth shut.

1009
01:12:07,430 --> 01:12:09,980
去年你泄露了最高机密 差点把我们全害死
You betrayed top secret information.

1010
01:12:10,010 --> 01:12:11,150
你在胡说什么?
What the hell are you talking about?

1011
01:12:11,190 --> 01:12:14,310
你把一切都告诉了你父亲 使整个计划处于危险之中
You told your father everything, put this entire plan in jeopardy.

1012
01:12:14,350 --> 01:12:17,400
幸好你父亲的嘴闭得比你紧
Good thing for you, the old man could keep his mouth shut better than you.

1013
01:12:17,430 --> 01:12:18,950
拜托 别这么吃惊
Oh, come on. Don't look so shocked.

1014
01:12:18,980 --> 01:12:20,490
我们必须监控所有人
We had to monitor everybody who knew.

1015
01:12:20,530 --> 01:12:22,520
不然怎么能把秘密保守到今天?
How do you think we kept it a secret for so long?

1016
01:12:22,860 --> 01:12:24,800
所以你就杀了所有想说出真相的人?
So you just killed anybody who tried to talk?

1017
01:12:25,160 --> 01:12:28,000
泄密的人不仅是国家的敌人
Anybody who tried to talk was not just an enemy of the state.

1018
01:12:28,050 --> 01:12:29,790
更是人类的公敌
They were an enemy of humanity.

1019
01:12:29,830 --> 01:12:32,160
卢浮宫博物馆馆长是人类公敌?
The director of the Louvre was an enemy of humanity?

1020
01:12:32,200 --> 01:12:34,560
他决定召开记者招待会 他就是
After he called a press conference, he was.

1021
01:12:35,460 --> 01:12:37,510
天啊 你想怎样呢?
Jesus, what did you think?

1022
01:12:37,540 --> 01:12:40,840
所有人通通都上船 手拉手唱赞歌?
We're all just gonna get on board, hold hands and sing Kumbaya?

1023
01:12:41,760 --> 01:12:44,000
给我坐下 系好安全带
Sit down and buckle up.

1024
01:12:53,230 --> 01:12:55,800
对不起 我父亲在指挥中心吗?
Excuse me, is my father in the Command Center?

1025
01:12:56,310 --> 01:12:58,400
总统先生刚打电话过来 威尔逊博士
President is on the line, Dr. Wilson.

1026
01:12:59,860 --> 01:13:01,300
谢谢
Thank you.

1027
01:13:08,030 --> 01:13:09,100
你在哪里?
Where are you?

1028
01:13:09,410 --> 01:13:12,870
如果我告诉你 你就不会上飞机了
You never would've gotten on that plane if I told you.

1029
01:13:15,370 --> 01:13:19,000
- 但你说过你会和我一起的 - 我的孩子 听我说
- But you said that you'd be here. - Darling, listen to me.

1030
01:13:19,130 --> 01:13:21,500
知道你可以活着
Do you understand how much strength it gives me

1031
01:13:22,040 --> 01:13:24,000
就是给我的最大鼓励
knowing that you will survive?

1032
01:13:25,340 --> 01:13:27,800
我现在唯一要做的事
The only thing left to do now,

1033
01:13:28,970 --> 01:13:31,220
就是告诉人民真相
is tell the truth to people.

1034
01:13:32,270 --> 01:13:34,400
至少他们知道后
At least if they know,

1035
01:13:37,060 --> 01:13:40,400
家人间还可以彼此告别
families can say goodbye to each other.

1036
01:13:41,110 --> 01:13:44,000
母亲能安慰她的孩子
A mother can comfort her children.

1037
01:13:46,530 --> 01:13:48,000
而父亲
And a father...

1038
01:13:50,530 --> 01:13:53,160
可以请求女儿原谅自己
can ask his daughter for forgiveness.

1039
01:14:02,340 --> 01:14:05,000
您准备好了就开始 总统先生
Whenever you're ready, Mr President.

1040
01:14:13,020 --> 01:14:15,400
美国同胞们
My fellow Americans,

1041
01:14:16,100 --> 01:14:18,800
这是我最后一次发表讲话
this will be the last time I address you.

1042
01:14:20,150 --> 01:14:24,800
正如大家知道的 灾难席卷了美国
As you know, catastrophe has struck our nation,

1043
01:14:26,740 --> 01:14:28,800
也将席卷整个世界
has struck the world.

1044
01:14:29,150 --> 01:14:31,460
真希望我可以告诉你们
I wish I could tell you

1045
01:14:31,490 --> 01:14:34,300
我们有能力抵御这场灾难
we could prevent the coming destruction.

1046
01:14:34,910 --> 01:14:36,500
但我们无能为力
We cannot.

1047
01:14:37,120 --> 01:14:40,400
今天 没有人是陌生人
Today, none of us are strangers.

1048
01:14:41,040 --> 01:14:44,420
今天 我们都是一家人
Today, we are one family,

1049
01:14:44,460 --> 01:14:47,880
一起走进黑暗
stepping into the darkness together.

1050
01:14:47,930 --> 01:14:51,100
我们可能信仰不同
We are a nation of many religions,

1051
01:14:51,140 --> 01:14:57,520
但我相信这句话 可以代表我们共同的信仰
but I believe these words reflect the spirit of all our faiths:

1052
01:14:57,810 --> 01:15:01,000
耶和华是我的牧者 我必...
"The lord is my Shepard. I shall... "

1053
01:14:57,810 --> 01:15:01,000
出自《圣经.诗篇23篇》

1054
01:15:02,650 --> 01:15:06,000
大家不要靠近门和窗户
People! Get away from the doors and windows.

1055
01:15:06,360 --> 01:15:08,600
我们怎么办? 你告诉我
What are we gonna do? You tell me.

1056
01:15:08,700 --> 01:15:11,700
- 西尔伯曼医生? - 塔玛拉!
- Dr. Silberman? - Tamara!

1057
01:15:11,750 --> 01:15:13,900
你怎么会在这?
What are you doing here?

1058
01:15:14,160 --> 01:15:15,450
她是我的病人 亲爱的
She's a patient, Honey.

1059
01:15:15,490 --> 01:15:19,080
不好意思 我的私人飞机停在外面
Excuse me, I have a private plane out there.

1060
01:15:19,120 --> 01:15:22,000
卡尔波夫! 尤里!
Karpov! Yuri!

1061
01:15:22,330 --> 01:15:24,590
你知道真相 你一直都知道
You knew. This whole time you knew.

1062
01:15:24,630 --> 01:15:27,170
你有办法离开 对吧? 你有飞机
You've got a way out of here, right? You got a plane?

1063
01:15:27,210 --> 01:15:29,800
带我的家人一起走 求你了!
My family, take us with you. Please!

1064
01:15:29,840 --> 01:15:31,900
老板 老板
Boss, boss.

1065
01:15:32,180 --> 01:15:34,010
我找到了一架飞机 一架安东诺夫
I found us a plane. An Antonov.

1066
01:15:34,050 --> 01:15:37,000
他们刚才要起飞 但控制塔不准他们起飞
They were just about to take off, but the tower didn't let them.

1067
01:15:37,080 --> 01:15:39,500
你会飞那家伙吗?
Can you still fly that thing?

1068
01:15:39,550 --> 01:15:43,200
- 没问题 老板 不过我需要一个副驾驶 - 完了
- Sure, Boss, but I need co-pilot. - No.

1069
01:15:43,470 --> 01:15:45,000
戈登是飞行员
Gordon's a pilot.

1070
01:15:45,910 --> 01:15:48,240
不 我不是 我不是
No, I'm not. I'm not.

1071
01:15:48,280 --> 01:15:51,070
他就是 很棒的飞行员 快走吧
Yes he is. Great pilot. Let's go.

1072
01:15:51,110 --> 01:15:53,630
太好了 我们走!
Good. Let's go!

1073
01:15:53,870 --> 01:15:56,300
杰克逊 别再说我是飞行员了
Jackson, stop saying I'm a pilot.

1074
01:15:58,160 --> 01:16:00,700
你们不能出去 回来!
You can't go out there. Come back!

1075
01:16:05,790 --> 01:16:08,210
后退 大家快后退!
Move back, people!

1076
01:16:13,890 --> 01:16:16,510
哇 真是架大飞机
Wow, that's a big plane.

1077
01:16:16,930 --> 01:16:19,560
俄罗斯造的
It's Russian.

1078
01:16:19,640 --> 01:16:21,730
大家快上去 快点!
Let's move everybody. Come on!

1079
01:16:26,730 --> 01:16:29,320
- 戈登 你在哪儿? - 我来了!
- Gordon, where are you? - Let's go!

1080
01:16:29,360 --> 01:16:31,400
快上来 戈登 快点!
Up here, Gordon. Hurry up!

1081
01:16:32,860 --> 01:16:35,530
我的上帝 又来了
Oh my God. Not again.

1082
01:16:35,080 --> 01:16:37,000
2012
拉斯维加斯车展

1083
01:16:42,790 --> 01:16:46,420
- 哇哦 好酷啊 - 拉斯维加斯车展
- Woah, look at these. - Las Vegas auto show.

1084
01:16:46,450 --> 01:16:49,300
我们还有贵宾卡
We had VIP tickets for this.

1085
01:16:49,350 --> 01:16:51,050
太好了 我们走吧
That's fantastic, let's go.

1086
01:16:51,090 --> 01:16:54,180
检查液压系统 我来平衡油箱
Check the main bus for hydraulics, I'll balance the tanks.

1087
01:16:54,220 --> 01:16:55,300
什么?
What?

1088
01:16:56,890 --> 01:16:59,140
好的 我尽力 我尽力试试
Okay, okay. I'm trying. Okay? I'm trying.

1089
01:17:01,310 --> 01:17:03,390
控制塔呼叫安东诺夫 你们到底在干什么?
Tower to Antonov, what the hell are you doing?

1090
01:17:03,430 --> 01:17:04,700
立刻停下来
Shut down immediately.

1091
01:17:12,440 --> 01:17:13,570
凯撒 乖
Caesar, shh.

1092
01:17:14,150 --> 01:17:17,200
我一说"走" 就把它推到底 明白吗?
When I say "go", we push all this down at once, okay?

1093
01:17:17,240 --> 01:17:18,830
- 明白 - 走!
- Okay. - Go!

1094
01:17:18,870 --> 01:17:23,080
安东诺夫 停止起飞 你没有起飞许可
Antonov, abort take-off. You do not have clearance.

1095
01:17:23,120 --> 01:17:25,600
重复 停止起飞!
I repeat, you must abort.

1096
01:17:31,960 --> 01:17:33,000
刚怎么回事?
What the hell was that?

1097
01:17:33,170 --> 01:17:35,500
不知道 但听起来不妙
I don't know, but it's not good.

1098
01:17:37,890 --> 01:17:39,800
- 推! - 正在推!
- Push! - Pushing!

1099
01:17:44,350 --> 01:17:46,700
要掉下去了! 要掉下去了!
We're going down! We're going down!

1100
01:17:55,450 --> 01:17:57,820
- 什么? - 肯定是泵出问题了! 你接手!
- What? - It must be the pump. Take over.

1101
01:17:57,870 --> 01:18:00,000
接手? 什么我接手?
Take over? What do you mean take over?

1102
01:18:02,540 --> 01:18:04,660
- 萨沙! - 别紧张
- Sasha! - Relax.

1103
01:18:10,000 --> 01:18:11,880
上帝! 我的上帝啊!
God! God! Jesus!

1104
01:18:14,920 --> 01:18:17,000
- 哦上帝! - 我搞定了
- Oh God! - I think I got it

1105
01:18:17,050 --> 01:18:19,720
- 萨沙 快来! - 深呼吸
- Sasha, now! - Take a deep breath.

1106
01:18:20,350 --> 01:18:21,810
拉!
Pull!

1107
01:18:23,430 --> 01:18:27,020
宝贝 快把屁股抬起来

1108
01:18:48,460 --> 01:18:50,200
那是埃菲尔铁塔?
Was that the Eiffel Tower?

1109
01:18:51,170 --> 01:18:53,400
大概是吧
I think so.

1110
01:19:00,390 --> 01:19:05,000
女士们先生们 我们正飞往中国
Ladies and Gentlemen. We're on our way to China.

1111
01:19:06,640 --> 01:19:09,200
好 非常好
Good. Very good.

1112
01:19:19,610 --> 01:19:24,400
不要相信那些传闻 尼玛

1113
01:19:24,950 --> 01:19:28,830
师傅 可丹增是我哥哥

1114
01:19:28,910 --> 01:19:32,290
他在造大船的隧道里工作

1115
01:19:34,800 --> 01:19:40,140
如果丹增说得没错 世界末日真的来了

1116
01:19:40,180 --> 01:19:44,560
以仁波切的智慧 您会怎么做?

1117
01:19:40,180 --> 01:19:44,560
仁波切是对西藏佛法成就者的尊称

1118
01:19:52,650 --> 01:19:56,190
已经满了 仁波切

1119
01:19:57,110 --> 01:19:58,570
别再倒了

1120
01:20:01,570 --> 01:20:09,080
就像这个杯子 你的内心被恐惧与猜疑所填满

1121
01:20:09,460 --> 01:20:15,000
想要看到智慧之光 你先要平静你的内心

1122
01:20:31,940 --> 01:20:33,900
注意离合器

1123
01:20:34,270 --> 01:20:36,690
不好挂档

1124
01:20:54,460 --> 01:20:55,860
奶奶

1125
01:20:56,170 --> 01:20:58,180
他爷爷 尼玛来了

1126
01:20:58,210 --> 01:21:00,050
奶奶 丹增让我带个消息

1127
01:21:00,090 --> 01:21:03,130
他叫我们去卓铭谷的工地找他

1128
01:21:04,200 --> 01:21:07,300
他说有办法带我们上船

1129
01:21:07,340 --> 01:21:09,220
你在说什么呢?

1130
01:21:09,260 --> 01:21:11,810
丹增不是在建大坝吗?

1131
01:21:14,400 --> 01:21:15,850
奶奶

1132
01:21:16,520 --> 01:21:19,940
其实他们在建大船 政府骗了我们

1133
01:21:20,690 --> 01:21:22,610
洪水就要来了

1134
01:21:23,280 --> 01:21:24,990
我们必须马上走

1135
01:21:25,160 --> 01:21:28,030
尼玛 谁借给你的车?

1136
01:21:28,780 --> 01:21:34,920
有一次我们坐船 你爷爷吐了一路

1137
01:21:35,920 --> 01:21:37,880
还是先吃饭吧

1138
01:21:43,000 --> 01:21:47,510
- 瞧 新款宾利 - 我爸爸订过一辆
- Hey, look, the new Bentley! - Our father had one on order.

1139
01:21:47,550 --> 01:21:49,400
本来明年就能拿到
He was supposed to get it next year.

1140
01:21:49,600 --> 01:21:52,890
但因为要坐大船 他又取消了
But then he canceled it. Because of the ships.

1141
01:21:52,930 --> 01:21:55,000
你们家有几辆车?
How many cars does your family have?

1142
01:21:56,100 --> 01:21:59,190
我妈的男朋友有辆保时捷
My mom's boyfriend has a Porsche.

1143
01:21:59,230 --> 01:22:01,860
我们的爸妈也离婚了
Our parents are divorced too.

1144
01:22:01,900 --> 01:22:03,990
是啊 我们对此也无能为力
Yeah, but there is nothing that we can do about that.

1145
01:22:04,030 --> 01:22:05,150
找到帽子了
Found a hat.

1146
01:22:05,900 --> 01:22:07,580
她很喜欢帽子
She has a thing for hats.

1147
01:22:07,800 --> 01:22:10,630
我在她这么大的时候也一样
I was just like that at her age.

1148
01:22:10,870 --> 01:22:12,750
帽子让我感到安全
They made me feel safe.

1149
01:22:13,000 --> 01:22:17,170
那么 你是怎么认识西尔伯曼医生的?
So, how did you meet Dr. Silberman?

1150
01:22:17,410 --> 01:22:19,630
很明显 和你认识他的方式不同
As you can see, not the same way you did.

1151
01:22:22,000 --> 01:22:26,130
我男朋友让我去隆胸
My boyfriend asked me to get them done.

1152
01:22:26,180 --> 01:22:27,500
他不是你丈夫?
He's not your husband?

1153
01:22:28,260 --> 01:22:32,470
不 我们没结婚 估计以后也不可能结婚
We are not married. And probably never will be.

1154
01:22:39,500 --> 01:22:41,200
给你孩子的
For the boys.

1155
01:22:45,800 --> 01:22:48,240
她们相处的不错
They seem to like each other.

1156
01:22:50,000 --> 01:22:52,000
是啊
Yeah, I guess.

1157
01:22:53,400 --> 01:22:56,400
说真的 卡尔波夫先生 你付了多少钱?
Tell me, Mr. Karpov, how much did you pay?

1158
01:22:56,580 --> 01:23:01,630
一个座位10亿欧元
One billion Euro. Per seat.

1159
01:23:02,300 --> 01:23:05,430
- 真夸张 - 是吗?
- That's disgusting. - Oh yeah?

1160
01:23:06,000 --> 01:23:10,400
你知道的 柯蒂斯 我以前不是生意人
You know, Curtis, I wasn't always a businessman.

1161
01:23:10,760 --> 01:23:12,400
我是个拳击手
I am a boxer.

1162
01:23:12,450 --> 01:23:17,000
我年轻时在摩尔曼斯克打拳
Was my only playing when I was boy back in Murmansk.

1163
01:23:17,070 --> 01:23:23,320
我的教练也叫尤里 他常常跟我说
And my coach, his name was also Yuri. He always said:

1164
01:23:23,360 --> 01:23:29,820
"如果有人想击倒你 那他必须先杀了你"
"If someone wants to beat you he has to kill you first."

1165
01:23:32,900 --> 01:23:34,500
说得好
That's very nice.

1166
01:23:35,700 --> 01:23:41,200
告诉我 如果你和我一样有钱 你会像我这样做吗?
But tell me, what would you have done if you were rich like me?

1167
01:23:41,600 --> 01:23:45,460
看 他们都是很棒的孩子
Look, they are wonderful children.

1168
01:23:47,000 --> 01:23:50,260
各位注意 我们计划在夏威夷加油
OK, guys. The plan is to refill in Hawaii,

1169
01:23:50,300 --> 01:23:52,300
请坐好并系上安全带
so sit down and buckle up.

1170
01:23:52,500 --> 01:23:54,300
剩下的交给我和戈登
Gordon and I will do the rest.

1171
01:23:57,000 --> 01:23:58,850
噢 上帝啊
Oh God.

1172
01:24:00,500 --> 01:24:02,190
叫他们过来
Go get the guys.

1173
01:24:04,500 --> 01:24:09,200
伙计们 有点问题... 你们也许该...
Guys, there's a... You might wanna...

1174
01:24:27,000 --> 01:24:31,180
- 这是哪儿? - 夏威夷
- What is that? - The state of Hawaii

1175
01:24:31,220 --> 01:24:35,720
不好 非常不好
Not good. That is not good.

1176
01:24:40,000 --> 01:24:43,450
- 我们还有多少油? - 不够了
- How much fuel do we have left? - Not enough.

1177
01:24:43,500 --> 01:24:47,800
我们得在中国南海附近迫降
We have to make a water landing somewhere in South China sea.

1178
01:24:47,850 --> 01:24:50,900
好极了 至少不用起落架
Great, at least we won't need a landing gear.

1179
01:24:50,950 --> 01:24:54,280
- 起落架怎么了? - 都落在拉斯维加斯了
- What about it? - We lost it all, in Vegas.

1180
01:25:04,900 --> 01:25:07,000
威尔逊博士 我可以进来吗?
Dr. Wilson, may I come in?

1181
01:25:07,100 --> 01:25:09,960
不好意思 恐怕我的心情不太好
I'm not a very good company, I'm afraid.

1182
01:25:10,500 --> 01:25:14,130
- 博士 - 叫我艾德里安就好
- Doctor... - Please, call me Adrian.

1183
01:25:19,500 --> 01:25:21,800
对于所有不能上船的人
All those people we left behind.

1184
01:25:22,100 --> 01:25:24,700
他们都没有机会了 对吗?
They don't stand a chance, do they?

1185
01:25:26,200 --> 01:25:29,570
我相信大自然会作出选择的
I believe that nature will choose for itself,

1186
01:25:29,610 --> 01:25:32,530
从它自身来决定谁该继续生存
from itself, what will survive.

1187
01:25:34,000 --> 01:25:37,000
就像你一样 保护那些伟大的艺术品
Just like you, preserving those great artworks.

1188
01:25:37,500 --> 01:25:41,500
人类的文化就是我们的灵魂 今晚它不会灭亡
Our culture is our soul, and that's not dying tonight.

1189
01:25:41,600 --> 01:25:45,600
拜托 我帮你们掩人耳目?
Come on, I contributed to this cover up?

1190
01:25:45,900 --> 01:25:49,100
达・芬奇 毕加索 这些艺术品都上船了
The Da Vinci, Picasso, they're in.

1191
01:25:49,200 --> 01:25:52,000
但如果你是无名小卒 你就没有机会
But if you're some nobody you don't stand a chance.

1192
01:25:52,900 --> 01:25:55,720
这不一定完全正确
It's not necessarily true.

1193
01:25:56,200 --> 01:26:00,500
你听过一个叫杰克逊・柯蒂斯的作家吗?
Did you ever hear of a writer called Jackson Curtis?

1194
01:26:00,600 --> 01:26:03,020
他写了一本书 《再见亚特兰蒂斯》
Wrote a book, "Farewell Atlantis".

1195
01:26:03,400 --> 01:26:06,400
他的这本书只卖出了500本
What do you think the chances are of an unknown writer

1196
01:26:06,500 --> 01:26:09,900
你觉得他的书能留存下来的概率是多少?
who barely sold 500 copies making it aboard this plane?

1197
01:26:11,400 --> 01:26:13,000
我不明白
I don't understand.

1198
01:26:13,050 --> 01:26:16,600
无论这是机会或者信念或者命运 这些都不重要
I mean call it chance or faith or nature, doesn't matter.

1199
01:26:16,650 --> 01:26:20,200
这本书已经是我们的遗产了 为什么?
This book is part of our legacy now. Why?

1200
01:26:20,800 --> 01:26:22,300
因为我正在读它
Because I'm reading it.

1201
01:26:26,200 --> 01:26:29,900
赫尔姆斯利博士 请马上到指挥中心
Dr. Helmsley, please report to the situation room.

1202
01:26:42,600 --> 01:26:44,000
喂 你是谁?

1203
01:26:44,100 --> 01:26:46,140
你好 打扰了
Hello, I'm sorry.

1204
01:26:46,350 --> 01:26:49,100
- 请问你是哪位? - 我是洋子・德尔加多
- Who is this? - This is Yoko Delgado.

1205
01:26:49,200 --> 01:26:51,500
你找我爹地吗?
Do you want to speak to my daddy?

1206
01:26:54,400 --> 01:26:56,200
是的 麻烦你了
Yes, please.

1207
01:26:56,300 --> 01:26:58,500
我要说是谁打来的呢?
Who should I say is calling?

1208
01:27:01,500 --> 01:27:06,800
- 就说是他爸爸 - 你是我的爷爷?
- Tell him, its his father. - You're my grandpa?

1209
01:27:06,900 --> 01:27:09,600
是的 宝贝 我是你爷爷
Yes, sweetheart, I am.

1210
01:27:11,600 --> 01:27:14,590
爹地 爹地 爷爷来电话了
Daddy, Daddy, grandpa is on the phone.

1211
01:28:18,280 --> 01:28:19,400
总统先生
Mr President, Sir.

1212
01:28:27,000 --> 01:28:30,000
- 怎么了 宝贝? - 她找不到她爸爸了
- What's the matter, sweety? - She can't find her daddy.

1213
01:28:32,200 --> 01:28:35,800
你们为什么不坐到沙发上去 那里舒服些 莎莉
Why don't you two get comfy on that couch? Sally.

1214
01:28:35,840 --> 01:28:37,050
过来帮帮她们
Come here and help them.

1215
01:28:38,800 --> 01:28:40,600
我去找你爸爸
I'll find your daddy.

1216
01:28:48,500 --> 01:28:50,800
谁负责登记失踪人员?
Who can help me with missing persons?

1217
01:28:51,000 --> 01:28:53,060
抱歉 老兄 我现在真的忙不过来
Sorry, man, I'm really busy right now.

1218
01:28:53,600 --> 01:28:57,200
我是说没问题 不好意思 总统先生
I mean of course, sir. Sorry, Mr President.

1219
01:28:57,300 --> 01:28:59,990
没关系 孩子 你干得很好
Don't worry about it, you're doing a great job, son.

1220
01:29:26,550 --> 01:29:29,100
- 怎么了? - 首都发生了9.4级地震
- What's happening? - The Capitol has been hit by a 9.4

1221
01:29:29,200 --> 01:29:30,500
我们和白宫失去了联系 长官
Lost communication with the White House, sir.

1222
01:29:30,600 --> 01:29:32,680
- 震中在哪里? - 北切萨皮克湾
- Where is it centered? - North Chesapeake Bay.

1223
01:29:37,000 --> 01:29:40,300
安海斯先生 俄罗斯总统打来电话
Mr. Anheuser, Russian president on the line, sir.

1224
01:29:40,800 --> 01:29:42,000
失陪一下
Excuse me.

1225
01:29:42,240 --> 01:29:44,500
我们刚刚进入中国领空
We just entered Chinese air space.

1226
01:29:46,200 --> 01:29:48,030
这是肯定的 总统先生
That's affirmative, Mr. President.

1227
01:29:48,070 --> 01:29:53,800
在恢复通讯之前 由我暂任总指挥
Until communication is restored, I suppose I am in command.

1228
01:29:54,000 --> 01:29:56,800
其他国家的元首也都在去中国的途中
It appears that all other heads of state are enroute,

1229
01:29:56,900 --> 01:29:59,300
除了意大利总理
with the exception of the Italian Prime Minister,

1230
01:29:59,500 --> 01:30:05,500
他也决定留下来向上天祈祷
Who has also decided to stay behind and trust in prayer.

1231
01:31:12,000 --> 01:31:14,800
地壳开始移动了 赫尔姆斯利博士
Earth's crust has begun to shift, Dr. Helmsley!

1232
01:31:14,900 --> 01:31:17,600
- 移动了多少? - 1.2度 还在移动
- By what degree? - 1.2 degree. Still moving.

1233
01:31:17,700 --> 01:31:18,800
那接下来会怎么样?
So, what happens next?

1234
01:31:18,900 --> 01:31:21,400
大陆位移结束之后
The movement of our land masses comes to a halt.

1235
01:31:21,500 --> 01:31:22,900
让我们看看仿真图
Let's see a simulation.

1236
01:31:23,960 --> 01:31:26,200
会形成巨大的海啸
Expect the formation of gigantic tsunamis.

1237
01:31:26,250 --> 01:31:29,340
和地震强度成正比
Proportional to the magnitude of corresponding quakes.

1238
01:31:35,100 --> 01:31:37,500
- 放大日本海的图像 - 是 长官
- Pull up the Japanese sea border. - Yes, sir.

1239
01:31:38,700 --> 01:31:41,200
我爸爸在那附近的一条游轮上
My dad's on a cruise ship out there.

1240
01:31:42,300 --> 01:31:44,600
不过我猜你早就知道了
But I guess you already knew that.

1241
01:31:45,900 --> 01:31:50,000
长官 我们监测到了两次深海地震 分别是7.9级和8.2级
Sir, we've recorded two underwater quakes at 7.9 and 8.2.

1242
01:32:07,500 --> 01:32:09,100
根据最新消息
From what we have just learned,

1243
01:32:09,200 --> 01:32:12,100
东京发生了极其强烈的地震
Tokyo seems to have taken the full force of the earthquake.

1244
01:32:12,300 --> 01:32:14,900
有消息称
At this point unconfirmed reports indicate that

1245
01:32:15,000 --> 01:32:17,500
日本大片陆地已沉入海底
large areas of land are under water.

1246
01:32:29,900 --> 01:32:30,900
托尼
Tony.

1247
01:32:32,000 --> 01:32:33,800
我打电话了
I called.

1248
01:32:36,800 --> 01:32:38,600
但已经晚了
I was too late.

1249
01:32:43,200 --> 01:32:46,300
可能他们逃出去了
Maybe they got out of town.

1250
01:32:46,400 --> 01:32:47,700
谁也说不准
You never know...

1251
01:33:17,080 --> 01:33:18,580
哈里!
Harry!

1252
01:34:16,300 --> 01:34:18,100
我来了 桃乐西
I'm coming home, Dorothy.

1253
01:34:45,400 --> 01:34:46,500
有信号吗?
Anything?

1254
01:34:48,200 --> 01:34:49,800
什么都没有
Nothing but static.

1255
01:34:49,860 --> 01:34:51,500
连紧急信号都没有
Not even an emergency signal.

1256
01:35:04,200 --> 01:35:07,200
不敢想像地面上发生了什么
Can't think about what's going on down there.

1257
01:35:14,200 --> 01:35:16,400
还记得我们以前露营时开的旧甲壳虫吗?
Remember that old Beetle we used to camp in?

1258
01:35:16,500 --> 01:35:18,100
你从来没把顶棚打开过
But you'd never get the roof up.

1259
01:35:19,600 --> 01:35:22,330
我们真该换辆车
We definitely traded up.

1260
01:35:25,000 --> 01:35:27,200
带孩子出去玩时
Tried to find our old spot at Yellowstone.

1261
01:35:27,300 --> 01:35:29,800
本想去黄石公园找我们的老地方 但是
When I went camping with the kids, but...

1262
01:35:30,400 --> 01:35:32,000
我找不到了
I couldn't find it.

1263
01:35:41,180 --> 01:35:43,200
你觉得人会变吗?
Do you think people change?

1264
01:35:43,700 --> 01:35:45,700
你指的是我吗?
By people, do you mean me?

1265
01:35:45,900 --> 01:35:46,900
对
Yes.

1266
01:35:47,000 --> 01:35:49,000
我们分手后 你觉得你变了吗?
Do you think you've changed since we separated?

1267
01:35:50,980 --> 01:35:53,300
我也经常吃麦片粥了
I seem to eat a lot more cereal now.

1268
01:35:57,300 --> 01:35:59,500
你以前总是埋头写书
You always had tunnel vision.

1269
01:36:00,500 --> 01:36:03,300
其他的什么你都不管
You could just block everything out and write.

1270
01:36:07,540 --> 01:36:09,710
也不管我们
You blocked us out.

1271
01:36:18,590 --> 01:36:20,090
你爱他吗?
Do you love him?

1272
01:36:22,930 --> 01:36:24,930
我很爱他
I love him enough.

1273
01:36:36,730 --> 01:36:40,150
全球的地面通讯都中断了 长官
All global ground communication is ceased, sir.

1274
01:36:43,990 --> 01:36:48,950
卫星只能接收到卓铭谷的信号
The only signals our satellites are picking up come from Cho Ming.

1275
01:36:49,620 --> 01:36:51,600
这算是个好消息
Well there's a piece of good news.

1276
01:36:52,280 --> 01:36:53,580
有新情况吗 博士?
Any updates, Doctor?

1277
01:36:53,670 --> 01:36:56,700
海啸将袭击各大洲
We expect the tsunamis to reach land fall on every continent.

1278
01:36:56,800 --> 01:37:00,500
卓铭谷也会在6小时后遭到海啸袭击
The Cho Ming area will be impacted in approximately 6 hours.

1279
01:37:01,840 --> 01:37:06,600
地壳已经向西南方向移动了23度
It looks like the crust have shifted by almost 23 degrees to the southwest.

1280
01:37:07,430 --> 01:37:08,900
数据显示
The data also shows

1281
01:37:09,000 --> 01:37:11,900
地球两极的磁场分布也颠倒了
the Earth's poles have reversed their magnetic fields.

1282
01:37:12,260 --> 01:37:14,270
这是它们的新位置
These are their new positions.

1283
01:37:16,400 --> 01:37:19,990
你的意思是 现在的北极
You're telling me that the North Pole

1284
01:37:20,020 --> 01:37:22,000
跑到威斯康辛州附近了?
is now somewhere in Wisconsin?

1285
01:37:22,320 --> 01:37:25,000
事实上 现在那里是南极
Actually, thats the South Pole now.

1286
01:37:29,500 --> 01:37:31,400
快撑不住了

1287
01:37:31,800 --> 01:37:33,400
出什么事了?

1288
01:37:33,500 --> 01:37:35,960
引擎熄火 6个废了2个
Engine failure. 2 of 6 are down.

1289
01:37:35,990 --> 01:37:37,300
你们必须做好准备
You must get ready.

1290
01:37:38,840 --> 01:37:42,340
- 还能撑多久? - 15分钟 运气好的话
- How long do we have? - 15 minutes. Maybe.

1291
01:37:44,090 --> 01:37:45,760
最好叫醒孩子们
Better wake up the kids.

1292
01:38:26,890 --> 01:38:28,220
你为什么讨厌戈登?
Why do you hate Gordon?

1293
01:38:32,930 --> 01:38:36,480
嘿 拜托
Hey. Come on.

1294
01:38:37,350 --> 01:38:41,690
你在说什么啊? 我不讨厌他
What are you talking about? I don't hate him.

1295
01:38:41,850 --> 01:38:43,610
反正你不喜欢他
You don't like him either

1296
01:38:43,690 --> 01:38:46,820
也许是因为我不了解他
That's because I don't know him well, maybe.

1297
01:38:46,950 --> 01:38:48,250
但我了解
But I do.

1298
01:38:48,280 --> 01:38:50,620
一旦你了解他 就会知道他真的很好
He's really nice once you get to know him.

1299
01:38:50,660 --> 01:38:52,200
你该多和他聊聊
You should talk to him more often.

1300
01:38:52,300 --> 01:38:55,080
你们会相处得很好的
You guys would get along really well.

1301
01:38:58,290 --> 01:39:00,500
你真的很喜欢他 对吧?
You like him a lot, huh?

1302
01:39:08,700 --> 01:39:12,260
我会尽力的 我保证 好吗?
I'll do my best. I promise. OK?

1303
01:39:13,640 --> 01:39:17,140
我真的为你感到骄傲
I'm really proud of you. Really proud of you.

1304
01:39:18,690 --> 01:39:20,610
快到了吗?
Is it time?

1305
01:39:22,300 --> 01:39:23,100
是的
Yeah

1306
01:39:23,300 --> 01:39:26,320
- 快准备好 - 穿救生衣 亚力克

1307
01:39:26,950 --> 01:39:28,320
爹地 怎么了?
Dad, what's wrong?

1308
01:39:28,740 --> 01:39:31,600
萨沙说要降落了 会有点颠簸
Sasha's gotta land. It's gonna be a little bumpy.

1309
01:39:31,650 --> 01:39:32,910
可能还会有点滑
Maybe a little wet.

1310
01:39:33,950 --> 01:39:35,000
爹地?
Daddy?

1311
01:39:41,500 --> 01:39:43,000
按住了
Hold her steady.

1312
01:40:00,060 --> 01:40:03,200
爹地 我真的不太会游泳
Daddy, I'm not a really good swimmer.

1313
01:40:03,300 --> 01:40:05,900
嘿 没关系 有救生衣呢
Hey, that's alright. It's what you got this for.

1314
01:40:06,700 --> 01:40:09,200
就像在家里的游泳池
It's like being in a swimming pool.

1315
01:40:09,300 --> 01:40:12,990
只是装备更酷 有哨子 还有灯
Only it's got more cool stuff. It's got a whistle, a light.

1316
01:40:14,200 --> 01:40:16,040
我以为我们要去中国
I thought we were going to China.

1317
01:40:16,830 --> 01:40:18,960
不 我们要在这里降落
No, we gotta land here.

1318
01:40:21,960 --> 01:40:23,300
这就是我们要做的
So that's what we're gonna do.

1319
01:40:23,350 --> 01:40:24,600
我们要呆在一起 对吧?
We're just gonna all stay together. Right?

1320
01:40:24,800 --> 01:40:26,300
不 我们都会死
No we're not, we're gonna die!

1321
01:40:26,250 --> 01:40:28,340
不 我们不会死
No, we're not.

1322
01:40:28,510 --> 01:40:29,930
保证吗?
Promise?

1323
01:40:30,050 --> 01:40:33,800
我向你们保证 不管发生什么 我们都会在一起
I promise you, we'll all stay together, no matter what happens.

1324
01:40:48,940 --> 01:40:51,610
杰克逊 尤里
Jackson, Yuri.

1325
01:40:53,740 --> 01:40:55,200
我想你们最好上来看看
I think you better come up here

1326
01:40:55,500 --> 01:40:57,700
等等 我去看看就回来
Hold on, I'm gonna go check this out.

1327
01:40:57,800 --> 01:40:59,000
- 爹地 爹地 - 我马上回来
- Dad, Dad! - I'll be right back

1328
01:41:00,000 --> 01:41:02,960
好了 嘿 系好安全带 快点
OK, hey, hey. We gotta buckle up. Let's go.

1329
01:41:04,210 --> 01:41:06,460
别问我怎么回事
Don't ask me how that happened.

1330
01:41:06,700 --> 01:41:07,700
我们现在不在海上
There is no more ocean,

1331
01:41:07,900 --> 01:41:10,300
而且我们就要到目的地了
and we're pretty close to where we wanted to go.

1332
01:41:10,400 --> 01:41:12,590
看来整个世界好像移动了1000英里
It's like the whole world shifted by 1000 miles.

1333
01:41:12,630 --> 01:41:15,390
准确的说是 1578英里
1578 to be exact.

1334
01:41:15,430 --> 01:41:17,770
这叫做"地壳漂移理论"
It's called "Earth Crust Displacement Theory"

1335
01:41:17,800 --> 01:41:19,810
哈普古德教授在1958年提出的
Professor Hapgood 1958.

1336
01:41:21,300 --> 01:41:22,800
真有你的 查理
Way to go, Charlie.

1337
01:41:25,940 --> 01:41:26,900
怎么了?
What was that?

1338
01:41:28,100 --> 01:41:31,030
最后两个引擎也熄火了
We just lost our last two engines.

1339
01:41:49,670 --> 01:41:51,300
我要在下面紧急降落
I'll shoot for that glacier.

1340
01:41:51,340 --> 01:41:52,630
会很颠簸
It's going to get rocky.

1341
01:41:52,670 --> 01:41:54,760
听好 这有些疯狂
Listen, it's gonna sound crazy,

1342
01:41:54,790 --> 01:41:56,850
但现在也只能这样做了
but here's what you have to do.

1343
01:42:02,000 --> 01:42:04,350
都起来! 跟我来!
Get up! Follow me!

1344
01:42:04,600 --> 01:42:06,560
尤里 我们要怎么做?
Yuri, what are you doing?

1345
01:42:06,800 --> 01:42:09,000
我们要开宾特利了
We are taking the Bentley!

1346
01:42:10,280 --> 01:42:12,820
等等! 还没到时候
Not yet! Not yet.

1347
01:42:14,860 --> 01:42:16,160
再等会儿
Almost there.

1348
01:42:17,160 --> 01:42:18,370
快上车!
Get in the car.

1349
01:42:29,000 --> 01:42:31,800
好了 开舱门! 快拉!
Okay, go now! Pull!

1350
01:42:42,430 --> 01:42:43,570
快走 杰克逊
Go, Jackson.

1351
01:42:43,600 --> 01:42:45,480
我们要等萨沙和戈登
We gotta wait for Sasha and Gordon.

1352
01:42:46,480 --> 01:42:50,500
快走! 确保所有人在着陆前都下飞机
Go! Make sure everybody gets off the plane before I touch down.

1353
01:42:50,600 --> 01:42:51,780
那你呢?
What about you?

1354
01:42:51,820 --> 01:42:55,820
不用管我 我要保证飞机降落
I'll be fine. I have to touch this plane down.

1355
01:42:56,910 --> 01:42:59,900
你还等什么? 快走! 快!
What are you waiting for? Go!

1356
01:43:15,880 --> 01:43:17,300
我看到他了 他来了
There he is. I see him!

1357
01:43:17,400 --> 01:43:19,310
- 萨沙呢? - 快点 我们走
- Where is Sasha? - Come on let's go.

1358
01:43:19,340 --> 01:43:20,980
- 萨沙在哪儿? - 他说他会没事的
- Where is Sasha? - He said he's fine

1359
01:43:21,010 --> 01:43:23,200
在飞机着陆前我们要出去
We should get out of here before he touches down.

1360
01:43:23,300 --> 01:43:25,500
不 不 不 我们得等他!
No, no, no. Don't go! We should wait for him.

1361
01:43:26,100 --> 01:43:27,850
杰克逊 快走
Go Jackson, go.

1362
01:43:29,500 --> 01:43:30,900
没法启动
It won't start.

1363
01:43:32,270 --> 01:43:35,030
通通闭嘴!
Shut up everybody!

1364
01:43:36,400 --> 01:43:38,360
引擎
Engine.

1365
01:43:38,400 --> 01:43:40,320
启动
Start.

1366
01:43:43,200 --> 01:43:46,330
声控的 很帅吧?
Voice control. Sold me on it.

1367
01:45:35,690 --> 01:45:38,190
下面 降落

1368
01:45:48,790 --> 01:45:51,790
欢迎来到中华人民共合国
Welcome, to the People's Republic of China.

1369
01:45:51,820 --> 01:45:53,790
很高兴能来 打招呼 孩子们
Good to be here. Say hi, kids.

1370
01:45:55,340 --> 01:45:58,550
- 你们的通行证是什么颜色? - 什么?
- What color are your passes? - What?

1371
01:45:58,600 --> 01:46:00,760
你们的登船通行证是什么颜色?
What color are your boarding passes?

1372
01:46:02,640 --> 01:46:05,100
我有绿色的
I have green cards.

1373
01:46:05,690 --> 01:46:08,560
- 上面有我和我儿子的名字 - 什么?
- For my boys and me. - What?

1374
01:46:11,860 --> 01:46:13,820
尤里? 尤里!
Yuri? Yuri!

1375
01:46:14,700 --> 01:46:17,820
尤里 没搞错吧 你在开玩笑对吗?
Yuri. It's a mistake. A joke, right?

1376
01:46:18,200 --> 01:46:23,870
怎么? 你以为我不知道你和萨沙的事?
What? You think I didn't know about you and Sasha?

1377
01:46:24,500 --> 01:46:28,670
愿上帝保佑那个混蛋的灵魂吧
May God bless that poor bastard's soul.

1378
01:46:33,760 --> 01:46:37,380
各位 抱歉了 祝你们好运
I'm sorry guys. Good luck.

1379
01:46:37,760 --> 01:46:39,680
走吧 孩子们
Come on, boys.

1380
01:46:41,140 --> 01:46:43,680
- 也许我们可以用钱贿赂他们 - 我有钱
- Maybe with money we could bribe them. - I do, I do.

1381
01:46:43,720 --> 01:46:45,560
你有10亿欧元吗?
You got a billion Euros?

1382
01:46:49,900 --> 01:46:54,610
威尔逊博士 我是迈克尔斯上校 美国方舟的船长
Dr. Wilson. I'm Captain Michaels, Skipper of the American ship.

1383
01:46:54,650 --> 01:46:57,200
请接受我对您父亲最诚挚的哀悼
Please accept my sincere condolences for your father.

1384
01:46:57,230 --> 01:46:58,270
谢谢你 船长
Thank you, Captain.

1385
01:46:59,860 --> 01:47:03,150
安海斯先生 你们是最后到的
Mr. Anheuser. Your party is the last to arrive.

1386
01:47:07,240 --> 01:47:09,580
船长 我们收到报告说方舟损坏严重
There's been reports of severe damage, Captain.

1387
01:47:09,610 --> 01:47:11,750
3号方舟的情况如何?
What's the status of Ark number 3?

1388
01:47:11,790 --> 01:47:13,830
全面评估尚未结束
We haven't done a complete assessment yet.

1389
01:47:13,860 --> 01:47:16,120
不过情况不容乐观
Looks like we lost it.

1390
01:47:25,780 --> 01:47:28,760
牙刷都不带 只带书
No toothbrush. Only books.

1391
01:47:29,700 --> 01:47:32,390
小时候 我爸爸经常出差
When I was a kid my dad was on the road a lot.

1392
01:47:33,730 --> 01:47:35,900
他总是给我留一箱书
He'd always leave me a box full of books.

1393
01:47:36,000 --> 01:47:37,730
每晚打电话监督我
Call me and cruise me.

1394
01:47:38,230 --> 01:47:41,770
每读完一本 我就可以得到一个冰淇淋蛋卷
I'd get an ice cream cone for every book I read so...

1395
01:47:41,810 --> 01:47:43,650
所以我小时候很胖
I was a fat kid.

1396
01:47:44,300 --> 01:47:46,800
真不敢相信
I find that very hard to believe.

1397
01:47:46,900 --> 01:47:50,900
是真的 我高中就读完了两千本书
No, its true, my high school carrier was 2000 books

1398
01:47:51,400 --> 01:47:53,200
一个女朋友没有
Zero girlfriends.

1399
01:47:54,240 --> 01:47:57,000
我上大学前甚至都没亲过男孩子
I didn't even kiss a boy until I was in college.

1400
01:47:57,740 --> 01:48:00,000
他们都很怕我爸爸
They were all too scared of my dad.

1401
01:48:48,090 --> 01:48:49,800
把这个项目交给中国是正确的
Leave it to the Chinese.

1402
01:48:50,000 --> 01:48:51,600
换作其他国家
I didn't think it was possible.

1403
01:48:51,700 --> 01:48:53,600
肯定无法完成
Not in the time we had.

1404
01:48:54,100 --> 01:48:56,100
那就是3号方舟 长官
That's Ark number 3, sir.

1405
01:48:56,470 --> 01:48:59,600
地壳移动时 顶棚坍塌了
The roof collapsed during the shifting of the Earth's crust.

1406
01:49:00,800 --> 01:49:02,100
天啊
Jesus Christ.

1407
01:49:03,440 --> 01:49:08,700
由于技术问题 3号方舟登船程序推迟
Boarding of Arc 3 will be delayed due to technical difficulties.

1408
01:49:12,320 --> 01:49:13,660
嘿 到底怎么了?
Hey, what's going on here?

1409
01:49:13,700 --> 01:49:16,300
我和我的儿子都有绿卡
I have a green card for my boys and me.

1410
01:49:16,400 --> 01:49:18,660
我要和你们的主管谈
I want to speak to your supervisor.

1411
01:49:18,700 --> 01:49:20,380
我就是主管
I am the supervisor.

1412
01:49:20,410 --> 01:49:23,500
回去跟其他拿绿卡的人一起排队 否则就拘留你
Get back with the other green cards, or I'll have you detained.

1413
01:49:25,750 --> 01:49:28,000
他说你和萨沙的事 是真的吗?
What he said about you and Sasha, is it true?

1414
01:49:28,100 --> 01:49:31,550
萨沙比尤里强100倍
Sasha was worth a hundred times a man like Yuri.

1415
01:49:31,700 --> 01:49:34,340
我早该听你的 西尔伯曼医生
I should have listened to you, Dr. Silberman.

1416
01:49:34,370 --> 01:49:39,500
其实我很喜欢我之前的样子 都是那个混蛋叫我去整形
I actually liked the way I looked before that monster talked me into it.

1417
01:49:39,600 --> 01:49:41,890
他还叫我打折呢
Did you know he asked me for a discount?

1418
01:49:41,930 --> 01:49:43,940
而且是分期付款
He payed in installments.

1419
01:49:43,970 --> 01:49:45,400
吝啬的混蛋
Cheap bastard.

1420
01:49:46,110 --> 01:49:47,400
听到了吗?
You hear that?

1421
01:49:50,500 --> 01:49:51,800
在那里!
Over there!

1422
01:49:55,160 --> 01:49:57,370
停车!
Stop!

1423
01:50:04,000 --> 01:50:06,400
停车! 停车!
Stop! Stop! Stop!

1424
01:50:10,590 --> 01:50:12,510
停车 停车

1425
01:50:20,310 --> 01:50:24,310
直升机马上就要降落机坪 请做好准备

1426
01:50:39,410 --> 01:50:41,200
这些人是怎么选出来的?
How were all these people chosen?

1427
01:50:41,300 --> 01:50:42,900
跟你的艺术品一样
Same way your Arc was.

1428
01:50:43,000 --> 01:50:44,000
由世界各地遗传专家来决定
By experts from all over the world.

1429
01:50:44,050 --> 01:50:47,000
我们需要需要保留下来的优秀基因
We had geneticists determine the perfect gene pool we need to repopulate.

1430
01:50:47,100 --> 01:50:48,790
这些人也是靠基因选出来的?
These people were chosen by geneticists?

1431
01:50:48,830 --> 01:50:52,600
所有的绿卡持有者 请到D4站台
All green card holders, please proceed to hangar D-4.

1432
01:50:52,670 --> 01:50:54,900
看来是支票让他们登船的
Looks to me like their check books got them on board.

1433
01:50:55,000 --> 01:50:56,300
说的没错 威尔逊博士
That's right, Dr. Wilson.

1434
01:50:56,350 --> 01:50:58,300
没有私人巨额资金的支持
Without billions of dollars from the private sector

1435
01:50:58,350 --> 01:51:00,500
就没有这整个项目
this entire operation would've been impossible.

1436
01:51:00,650 --> 01:51:01,800
我们竟然还卖票?
We sold tickets?

1437
01:51:02,100 --> 01:51:03,900
那这些工人呢?
What about all these workers?

1438
01:51:04,400 --> 01:51:05,900
他们能上船吗?
They all get passes?

1439
01:51:06,100 --> 01:51:10,300
想说什么? 人生不公平? 这就是你想说的?
What? Life isn't fair? Is that it?

1440
01:51:10,400 --> 01:51:13,300
要是你想让这些中国工人上船
If you want to donate your passes to a couple of Chinese workers,

1441
01:51:13,400 --> 01:51:15,100
你尽可以捐出你的通行证
you be my guest.

1442
01:51:15,700 --> 01:51:17,900
船长 我要一个出发前的简报
Captain, I want a pre-launch briefing.

1443
01:51:18,000 --> 01:51:19,400
每个国家都要有
All international teams present.

1444
01:51:54,280 --> 01:51:56,150
搞什么鬼?
What the hell?

1445
01:51:59,370 --> 01:52:02,400
搞什么? 这里可以挤10个人!
What is this? They could've fit 10 people in here.

1446
01:52:07,660 --> 01:52:09,440
萨特南来电

1447
01:52:09,800 --> 01:52:11,300
萨特南 你在哪儿?
Satnam, where are you?

1448
01:52:11,720 --> 01:52:14,130
- 在南畔高原 - 什么?
- On the Nampan Plateau. - What?

1449
01:52:16,050 --> 01:52:18,510
海啸正在从东面过来
There's a tidal wave coming from the east.

1450
01:52:18,540 --> 01:52:19,720
巨大无比
It's gigantic.

1451
01:52:19,890 --> 01:52:21,300
萨特南 出什么事了?
Satnam, what happened?

1452
01:52:21,720 --> 01:52:23,600
没人来接我们 艾德里安
We never got picked up, Adrian.

1453
01:52:23,630 --> 01:52:25,850
飞机根本没来
The airlift never came.

1454
01:52:27,730 --> 01:52:29,190
永别了 我的朋友
Goodbye, my friend.

1455
01:52:30,270 --> 01:52:36,000
萨特南
Satnam

1456
01:52:58,800 --> 01:53:01,590
- 玛丽 我们的设备在哪儿? - 在那边
- Mary, Mary, where are we set up? - Over there.

1457
01:53:06,200 --> 01:53:09,300
- 给我印度南畔高原的卫星图像 - 好的 马上
- Give me the satellite images from Napam, India. - OK, right away.

1458
01:53:09,640 --> 01:53:10,400
怎么了?
What's happening?

1459
01:53:11,560 --> 01:53:15,800
萨特南说有另一股海啸 从东面过来
Satnam was talking about another wave, coming from the east.

1460
01:53:19,200 --> 01:53:20,600
圣母玛利亚
Holy mother of God.

1461
01:53:20,780 --> 01:53:22,200
洪水会提前到来?
So the flooding will hit earlier?

1462
01:53:22,300 --> 01:53:24,950
你的意思是 第二股海啸就要来了?
You are telling me that the second wave is closer?

1463
01:53:24,990 --> 01:53:26,080
输入新的数据
Plug in the new data.

1464
01:53:27,910 --> 01:53:29,540
没有人去接萨特南!
Satnam didn't get picked up.

1465
01:53:29,570 --> 01:53:30,540
什么?
What?

1466
01:53:30,750 --> 01:53:33,380
现在这么乱 很多人都没法接
A lot of people didn't get picked up in this chaos.

1467
01:53:33,710 --> 01:53:35,760
这不是阴谋 赫尔姆斯利
This is not a conspiracy, Helmsley.

1468
01:53:35,790 --> 01:53:38,700
你的预测也不全都准确 对吧 博士?
Your predictions haven't exactly panned out, have they, Doctor?

1469
01:53:38,830 --> 01:53:41,130
准备好了
It's ready.

1470
01:53:42,800 --> 01:53:45,100
天啊 1500米高
Oh God, its 1500 meters high.

1471
01:53:46,220 --> 01:53:47,680
还有多久会到这里?
When will it get here?

1472
01:53:48,220 --> 01:53:49,350
告诉我 赫尔姆斯利 还有多久会到?
Talk to me, Hemsley, when will it hit?

1473
01:53:49,390 --> 01:53:51,000
打开倒计时
Adjust the countdown.

1474
01:54:07,450 --> 01:54:10,750
距离冲击时间还有28分10秒
28 minutes, 10 seconds to impact.

1475
01:54:10,780 --> 01:54:11,580
天啊
My God.

1476
01:54:12,000 --> 01:54:13,000
船长
Captain.

1477
01:54:13,300 --> 01:54:15,500
我要立刻和其他国家的元首谈谈
I need to speak to the other heads of state immediately.

1478
01:54:15,550 --> 01:54:17,220
- 马上 泰勒? - 是 船长
- Right away. Taylor? - Aye, Captain

1479
01:54:17,250 --> 01:54:20,840
4号方舟待命 6号方舟待命 7号方舟待命
Standing by. Ark 6, stand by. Ark 7, stand by.

1480
01:54:20,880 --> 01:54:23,500
我是卡尔・安海斯 4号方舟的代理指挥
This is Carl Anheuser acting CIC on 4,

1481
01:54:23,550 --> 01:54:24,150
是 长官
Yes sir

1482
01:54:24,200 --> 01:54:26,430
请求召开T-99紧急会议
Requesting emergency conference T-99.

1483
01:54:47,000 --> 01:54:49,200
他非常喜欢你 你知道吗?
He thinks the world of you, you know that?

1484
01:54:51,750 --> 01:54:53,400
他是个好孩子
He's a great little man.

1485
01:54:54,460 --> 01:54:55,580
是的
Yeah

1486
01:55:03,920 --> 01:55:06,000
我一直想拥有自己的家庭
I always wanted to have a family of my own.

1487
01:55:10,010 --> 01:55:11,720
你很幸运 杰克逊
You're a lucky man, Jackson.

1488
01:55:13,140 --> 01:55:14,520
你一定要记住
Don't ever forget it.

1489
01:55:30,910 --> 01:55:31,990
他们是谁?

1490
01:55:32,450 --> 01:55:34,200
我们在路上遇到的

1491
01:55:34,240 --> 01:55:36,100
送他们回去!

1492
01:55:42,050 --> 01:55:46,500
我是大喇嘛仁波切的弟子

1493
01:55:46,900 --> 01:55:48,500
你知道我不能这么做

1494
01:55:50,350 --> 01:55:51,800
你不用带我们所有人走
You don't have to take all of us.

1495
01:55:51,920 --> 01:55:54,300
只要带上我的孩子就行 求求你了
Please just take my children. I'm begging you.

1496
01:55:54,770 --> 01:55:56,360
我为什么要这么做?
Why should I do that?

1497
01:55:56,390 --> 01:56:00,600
你不也想救你的家人吗? 求你了!
Same reason you sent for your family. Please!

1498
01:56:00,900 --> 01:56:03,480
请带上孩子 不用管我们
Please just the children, you don't have to take us.

1499
01:56:03,520 --> 01:56:04,490
求你了!
Please!

1500
01:56:07,240 --> 01:56:10,570
求你了 上帝啊!
Please. Oh my God.

1501
01:56:13,240 --> 01:56:17,080
求你了 我不知道你是否听得懂
Please. I don't know if you can understand what I'm saying.

1502
01:56:17,120 --> 01:56:19,750
但我们都是母亲 求你了
As a mother, I'm begging you.

1503
01:56:19,790 --> 01:56:21,250
带上孩子吧
Please take them.

1504
01:56:22,590 --> 01:56:23,590
求你了
Please.

1505
01:56:23,900 --> 01:56:29,430
丹增 我们都是大地的子女

1506
01:56:30,260 --> 01:56:33,720
奶奶 人太多 计划就行不通了

1507
01:56:33,760 --> 01:56:37,000
带他们所有人一起走

1508
01:56:37,200 --> 01:56:38,500
带上他们

1509
01:56:48,820 --> 01:56:50,660
所有建筑工人马上撤离

1510
01:56:50,700 --> 01:56:52,490
所有工作人员做好准备

1511
01:56:52,830 --> 01:56:57,040
请所有建筑工人马上撤离

1512
01:56:57,080 --> 01:56:59,420
所有机组人员马上登船

1513
01:56:59,750 --> 01:57:01,600
他们把门打开了
They're opening the mountain.

1514
01:57:01,800 --> 01:57:04,500
他们要弃我们而去
They are leaving without us.

1515
01:57:06,170 --> 01:57:07,930
退后 你听见没有!
Get back. What did I tell you!

1516
01:57:07,970 --> 01:57:11,600
他们也要把你丢下了 看 傻瓜!
They are leaving you behind too. Look, idiot.

1517
01:57:25,480 --> 01:57:27,400
跟我来
Follow me.

1518
01:57:34,120 --> 01:57:37,000
我们得快点 他们要走了

1519
01:57:39,710 --> 01:57:42,170
启动安全程序
Initiating security procedures.

1520
01:57:47,550 --> 01:57:50,260
打扰下 艾德里安・赫尔姆斯利在哪儿?
Excuse me. Where can I find Adrian Helmsley?

1521
01:57:50,290 --> 01:57:51,630
在船上 跟我来
He's on the bridge. This way.

1522
01:57:55,890 --> 01:57:57,100
丹增 等等

1523
01:57:58,520 --> 01:58:00,520
奶奶 我们就快到了

1524
01:58:00,730 --> 01:58:02,670
压力正常吗 安东?
Green lights on pressure, Mr. Anton?

1525
01:58:02,700 --> 01:58:04,610
一切正常 船长
Green lights across the board, Captain.

1526
01:58:16,740 --> 01:58:17,950
为什么会有锚?
Why do they have anchors?

1527
01:58:17,990 --> 01:58:21,160
因为这不是太空船 是方舟
Because they're not space ships. They're Arcs.

1528
01:58:21,620 --> 01:58:22,790
快走吧
Let's go.

1529
01:58:35,220 --> 01:58:36,640
总统先生
Mr. President.

1530
01:58:37,680 --> 01:58:38,680
看看这个
You've got to see this.

1531
01:59:19,970 --> 01:59:21,520
启动加固装置
Engage the support mechanisms.

1532
01:59:21,560 --> 01:59:23,600
是 船长 启动加固装置
Aye-aye, Captain. Engaging supports.

1533
01:59:23,700 --> 01:59:25,480
这些支架大概能
Just exactly how long are these things

1534
01:59:25,530 --> 01:59:27,100
支持我们多久 船长?
expected to hold us in place, Captain?

1535
01:59:27,140 --> 01:59:30,900
它们只能抵抗第一波海啸的冲击 安海斯先生
They're just meant to withstand the first impact of the waves, Mr. Anheuser.

1536
01:59:48,210 --> 01:59:51,170
下去 奥列格 你先走
Down there Oleg, you go first.

1537
01:59:56,470 --> 01:59:57,720
凯撒
Caesar!

1538
02:00:04,350 --> 02:00:05,270
凯撒
Caesar!

1539
02:00:14,780 --> 02:00:16,700
凯撒 非常好!

1540
02:00:18,490 --> 02:00:21,910
好孩子 到妈妈这来
Good, good boy. Come to Mommy.

1541
02:00:21,940 --> 02:00:22,990
凯撒!
Caesar!

1542
02:00:23,740 --> 02:00:25,910
妈咪 塔玛拉呢?
Mommy, where's Tamara?

1543
02:00:28,210 --> 02:00:29,960
爸爸 快看!

1544
02:00:32,840 --> 02:00:34,590
- 塔玛拉 - 马上就来
- Tamara! - I'm coming.

1545
02:00:43,010 --> 02:00:44,010
接住!
Take it!

1546
02:01:11,080 --> 02:01:13,600
上帝啊 外面怎么回事?
Oh my god, what's happening out there?

1547
02:01:15,420 --> 02:01:18,670
安海斯说服了各国元首 马上启航
Anheuser convinced the other heads of state to launch.

1548
02:01:22,010 --> 02:01:23,500
安霍伊泽先生
Mr. Anheuser

1549
02:01:25,390 --> 02:01:27,390
必须停止外面的悲剧
We have to stop this madness.

1550
02:01:28,230 --> 02:01:30,230
让其它船都能看到我
Make sure the other bridges can see me.

1551
02:01:30,800 --> 02:01:31,700
你要干什么?
What do you think you're doing?

1552
02:01:31,800 --> 02:01:33,100
我知道我要干什么 打开吧
I know exactly what I'm doing. Turn it on.

1553
02:01:35,770 --> 02:01:37,860
女士们先生们 我是艾德里安・赫尔姆斯利博士
Ladies and Gentleman, this is Dr. Adrian Helmsley

1554
02:01:37,900 --> 02:01:41,070
已故总统威尔逊的首席科学顾问
Chief science adviser to the late President Wilson.

1555
02:01:41,160 --> 02:01:43,500
把声音开大点 霍夫曼先生
Could you please turn up the volume, Mr. Hoffman.

1556
02:01:44,000 --> 02:01:46,500
我知道为了保存人类的文明
I know we've all been forced to make difficult decisions

1557
02:01:46,550 --> 02:01:48,300
我们必须做出困难的抉择
to save our human civilization.

1558
02:01:48,300 --> 02:01:51,330
但作为人类 就意味着要相互关心
But to be human means to care for each other

1559
02:01:51,370 --> 02:01:55,500
所谓文明 就是要共同去创造更美好的生活
and civilization means to work together to create a better life.

1560
02:01:55,590 --> 02:01:57,890
如果是这样 那我们此时的行为
If that's true, then there's nothing human

1561
02:01:57,920 --> 02:02:01,010
就没有一丝人性和文明可言
and nothing civilized about what we're doing here.

1562
02:02:01,040 --> 02:02:03,590
赫尔姆斯利博士的热情令人钦佩
Dr. Helmsley's passion is admirable,

1563
02:02:03,760 --> 02:02:05,100
但我不得不提醒大家
But I remind you that

1564
02:02:05,200 --> 02:02:08,190
我们的资源有限 而且时间紧迫
we have very limited resources and extremely limited time.

1565
02:02:08,220 --> 02:02:12,800
扪心自问 我们能袖手旁观 看着这些人去死吗?
Ask yourselves, can we really stand by and watch these people die?

1566
02:02:13,650 --> 02:02:15,730
两天前我读到一句话
I read a quote two days ago.

1567
02:02:15,860 --> 02:02:18,150
作者现在可能已经死了 但他说
The author is probably dead by now. But he said:

1568
02:02:18,190 --> 02:02:21,130
"等到我们不再为他人而战时"
"The moment we stop fighting for each other"

1569
02:02:21,160 --> 02:02:24,070
"我们也就失去了人性"
"That's the moment that we lose our humanity."

1570
02:02:24,200 --> 02:02:25,370
为了拯救人类
And in order to save the human race,

1571
02:02:25,410 --> 02:02:28,040
我们制定了这个计划 并遵守着
we have and obligation to stick to this plan

1572
02:02:28,080 --> 02:02:31,290
这里的各国元首都签字同意了
which every nation on this flotilla signed up for.

1573
02:02:31,320 --> 02:02:33,750
他们现在只能听天由命!
They're in God's hands now.

1574
02:02:35,630 --> 02:02:38,130
军官 你把它关掉
Officer, you turn that off.

1575
02:02:39,130 --> 02:02:40,340
这是命令 关掉!
That is an order, sailor. Turn it off!

1576
02:02:40,380 --> 02:02:42,130
你敢关掉试试 年轻人!
Don't you dare touch that button, young man!

1577
02:02:42,170 --> 02:02:45,050
你们通通都疯了吗?
Have you completely lost your mind?

1578
02:02:45,390 --> 02:02:46,350
看看时间
Look at the clock!

1579
02:02:46,550 --> 02:02:49,100
我们只有可怜的15分钟了!
We have barely 15 minutes left!

1580
02:02:49,390 --> 02:02:51,700
你能为人类的灭绝负责吗?
Do you want to be responsible for the extinction of the human race?

1581
02:02:51,760 --> 02:02:53,270
你能负责吗 艾德里安?
Can you handle that, Adrian?

1582
02:02:53,980 --> 02:02:55,900
有一位年轻的印度天体物理学家
There's a young astrophysicist from India

1583
02:02:55,950 --> 02:02:57,700
我们能在这儿都是他的功劳
who's the reason we are all here.

1584
02:02:57,750 --> 02:02:59,000
噢 得了吧
Oh, for God's sake.

1585
02:02:59,320 --> 02:03:01,830
是他发现了这一切
He's the one who discovered it all.

1586
02:03:01,860 --> 02:03:05,200
是他把所有线索连在一起 是他救了我们所有人
He connected all the dots, we all owe him our lives.

1587
02:03:05,700 --> 02:03:06,500
我刚刚得知
I just learned that

1588
02:03:06,550 --> 02:03:10,800
他和他的家人在印度东部发生的海啸中丧生
he was killed with his family in a Tsunami in eastern India.

1589
02:03:12,710 --> 02:03:14,500
他是我的好朋友
He was my friend.

1590
02:03:15,580 --> 02:03:17,500
他就这样白白的死了
And he died in vain.

1591
02:03:18,290 --> 02:03:21,420
那里的所有人都白死了
Everybody out there has died in vain.

1592
02:03:21,590 --> 02:03:25,200
如果我们用如此残酷的方式开创未来
If we start our future with an act of cruelty,

1593
02:03:26,800 --> 02:03:29,500
我们怎么向孩子交代?
what will you tell your children?

1594
02:03:30,400 --> 02:03:32,400
他们又怎么向下一代交代?
What will they tell theirs?

1595
02:03:34,890 --> 02:03:38,940
如果我父亲在这里 他不会袖手旁观
If my father were here, he would open the gates.

1596
02:03:45,700 --> 02:03:48,320
俄罗斯人民以及
The people of Russia along with,

1597
02:03:49,370 --> 02:03:50,700
中国
China

1598
02:03:52,540 --> 02:03:54,370
和日本
and Japan

1599
02:03:54,410 --> 02:03:55,370
同意
Agree

1600
02:03:56,750 --> 02:03:59,080
把门打开!
To open the gates!

1601
02:04:00,540 --> 02:04:04,970
英国 西班牙 法国 加拿大 德国
The United Kingdom, Spain, France, Canada, Germany,

1602
02:04:05,000 --> 02:04:09,300
我想我也可以代表意大利总理
and I believe I may also speak for the Italian Prime Minister,

1603
02:04:09,680 --> 02:04:13,000
我们赞成让这些人进来
We vote to let these people come in.

1604
02:04:18,480 --> 02:04:20,300
迈克尔斯船长
Captain Michaels.

1605
02:04:21,770 --> 02:04:23,600
请开门
Please

1606
02:04:26,780 --> 02:04:28,370
我是船长
This is your Captain.

1607
02:04:28,410 --> 02:04:31,700
请稍候 我们将打开大门
In a few moments, we will open the gates.

1608
02:04:39,210 --> 02:04:41,960
好臭啊
Phew, it stinks.

1609
02:05:00,480 --> 02:05:02,900
- 他们正在开门 - 快! 快!
- They are opening the gate. - Go! Go!

1610
02:05:02,930 --> 02:05:04,860
诺亚 快点!
Noah. Move it!

1611
02:05:05,400 --> 02:05:07,600
诺亚! 诺亚!
Noah! Noah!

1612
02:05:18,870 --> 02:05:20,960
妈妈 出事了
Mom, something happened.

1613
02:05:21,000 --> 02:05:22,000
坚持住!
Hold on!

1614
02:05:24,800 --> 02:05:26,130
坚持住!
Hold on!

1615
02:05:28,670 --> 02:05:31,220
戈登 抓紧 他妈的! 把手给我!
Gordon, hold on. God damn it! Give me your hand! Give me your hand!

1616
02:05:31,250 --> 02:05:32,400
- 把手给我! - 救我!
- Reach for it! - Help me!

1617
02:05:32,500 --> 02:05:33,000
拉住我的手
Reach for it!

1618
02:05:37,640 --> 02:05:39,730
戈登!
Gordon!

1619
02:05:48,150 --> 02:05:49,700
快爬上去 快爬!

1620
02:06:23,480 --> 02:06:24,770
门怎么了?
What's wrong with the gate?

1621
02:06:25,110 --> 02:06:27,500
好像是门没有完全打开 我们正在检查
Looks like it didn't run the full cycle. We're checking it out.

1622
02:06:36,370 --> 02:06:39,000
距离冲击还有四分钟
4 minutes to impact.

1623
02:07:24,920 --> 02:07:28,040
- 我们满载了 船长 - 那就关门 马上!
- We're all loaded, Captain. - Then let's lock it up. Now!

1624
02:07:38,010 --> 02:07:41,390
奥列格 抓住我的手
Oleg! Grab my hand!

1625
02:07:41,430 --> 02:07:42,680
奥列格
Oleg!

1626
02:08:13,200 --> 02:08:15,200
有东西卡住了液压装置 船长
Something's jamming the hydraulics, Captain.

1627
02:08:15,270 --> 02:08:16,500
看在上帝的份上 快把故障排除
Well then get it out for Christ sake.

1628
02:08:16,550 --> 02:08:19,300
门不关上我们就没法启动引擎
I can't fire up the engines until we get a good seal on that gate.

1629
02:08:20,050 --> 02:08:22,470
船长 有人闯入动物区
Captain, we have a breach in the zoological bay.

1630
02:08:22,640 --> 02:08:24,770
- 可以放大吗? - 可以
- Can you zoom in? - Yeah.

1631
02:08:28,600 --> 02:08:30,100
我认识那几个孩子
I know those kids.

1632
02:08:30,150 --> 02:08:32,480
怎么回事? 到底发生了什么?
What is happening? What's going on?

1633
02:08:32,730 --> 02:08:34,200
他们从哪儿进来的?
Where did they come from?

1634
02:08:36,450 --> 02:08:38,450
在那里 从液压舱进来的
There. Through the hydraulic chamber.

1635
02:08:38,570 --> 02:08:39,910
船长 找到故障原因了
Captain, I think we found the problem!

1636
02:08:39,940 --> 02:08:42,490
- 他们是谁? - 等等!
- Who are these people? - No, wait!

1637
02:08:42,910 --> 02:08:43,740
那个人受伤了
He's injured.

1638
02:08:44,000 --> 02:08:45,000
可能出事了
Something must've gone wrong.

1639
02:08:45,000 --> 02:08:47,800
可能出事了? 可能...
Something must've gone wrong? Something must've gone...

1640
02:08:47,870 --> 02:08:50,400
你在开玩笑吗? 当然出事了!
Are you kidding me? Of course something went wrong!

1641
02:08:50,500 --> 02:08:52,500
应该恭喜你们俩
You know, congratulations to the both of you.

1642
02:08:52,600 --> 02:08:53,600
把我们全害死也没关系
Might have gotten us all killed,

1643
02:08:53,650 --> 02:08:56,260
只要你问心无愧 对吧 赫尔姆斯利?
but as long as your conscience is clean, right Helmsley?

1644
02:08:56,290 --> 02:08:58,170
船长 派紧急救援小队下去
Captain, get an emergency team down there,

1645
02:08:58,210 --> 02:08:59,600
我会在液压舱和他们会合
I'll meet them at the hydraulics chamber.

1646
02:08:59,700 --> 02:09:01,000
- 你知道怎么走吗? - 知道
- You know your way around here? - Yeah

1647
02:09:01,050 --> 02:09:02,200
我们走
Let's go!

1648
02:09:02,250 --> 02:09:04,300
距离冲击还有一分钟
1 minute to impact.

1649
02:09:18,030 --> 02:09:18,780
船长?
Captain?

1650
02:09:19,280 --> 02:09:21,000
卓明谷机场已经被摧毁
Cho Ming airfield has been hit.

1651
02:09:21,620 --> 02:09:25,660
- 启动紧急通讯系统 泰勒 - 可以了 船长
- Put me on emergency comm, Mr. Taylor. - You're on it, Captain.

1652
02:09:26,160 --> 02:09:28,370
大家注意 我是船长
This is the Captain speaking

1653
02:09:28,410 --> 02:09:31,210
我们马上就会遭到洪水冲击
We expect to be impacted by water shortly.

1654
02:09:31,420 --> 02:09:32,280
我们得走这里
We need to go this way.

1655
02:09:54,150 --> 02:09:57,400
所有控制台准备接受冲击
All stations prepare for impact.

1656
02:10:43,030 --> 02:10:45,500
冲击压力逼近80帕
Impact pressure just climbed 80 Pascal.

1657
02:10:45,530 --> 02:10:48,300
表面传感器受到0.2密尔的表面压力
Surface compression of valve sensors, Captain.

1658
02:10:48,350 --> 02:10:50,000
我找到赫尔姆斯利博士了
I tracked Dr. Helmsley.

1659
02:10:50,870 --> 02:10:51,250
在那儿
There!

1660
02:10:55,670 --> 02:10:58,590
让开! 让一下! 让一下!
Out of the way! Excuse me. Excuse me.

1661
02:10:59,340 --> 02:11:01,630
丹增 快到了

1662
02:11:02,340 --> 02:11:04,050
尼玛 怎么了?

1663
02:11:06,140 --> 02:11:07,060
塔玛拉!
Tamara!

1664
02:11:07,100 --> 02:11:09,520
把孩子们带过去
Will you take the kids please?

1665
02:11:09,850 --> 02:11:11,020
怎么走?
Which way?

1666
02:11:11,180 --> 02:11:15,200
我们过不去 船尾进水了
We can't get there! Water is entering the stern.

1667
02:11:15,500 --> 02:11:19,200
船后面淹掉后 会自动开始逐舱封闭
The rear of this ship is flooded and will seal up one compartment at a time.

1668
02:11:19,650 --> 02:11:21,150
戈登呢?
Where's Gordon?

1669
02:11:22,490 --> 02:11:23,530
不
No?

1670
02:11:25,570 --> 02:11:27,550
我们得回去
We gotta go back!

1671
02:11:27,590 --> 02:11:29,540
我们必须回去
We have to go back!

1672
02:11:33,080 --> 02:11:34,330
妈咪
Mommy!

1673
02:11:35,290 --> 02:11:36,790
- 救命! - 妈咪!
- Help! - Mommy!

1674
02:11:45,680 --> 02:11:47,000
快爬过去 莉莉
Go over, Lilly!

1675
02:11:50,220 --> 02:11:52,680
凯撒! 莉莉 带上它!
Caesar! Lilly, take him!

1676
02:11:54,850 --> 02:11:57,020
妈咪!
Mommy!

1677
02:12:03,990 --> 02:12:06,360
还有别的路到液压舱吗?
Is there another way to the hydraulics chamber?

1678
02:12:06,570 --> 02:12:07,530
这梯子通到哪儿?
Where does this ladder go?

1679
02:12:07,570 --> 02:12:10,660
- 通向动物区 - 好 快走!
- To the zoological bay. - Okay, let's go!

1680
02:12:16,540 --> 02:12:20,090
教授 那是空军一号
Professor? It's Air Force One.

1681
02:12:37,230 --> 02:12:39,060
中锚被击中了
The mid-ship anchor support is hit.

1682
02:12:39,150 --> 02:12:40,590
可以加固吗?
Can you stabilize it?

1683
02:12:40,620 --> 02:12:42,020
尾锚也不行了
The bow anchor is giving in.

1684
02:13:01,500 --> 02:13:03,400
船长 涡轮没有反应
Captain, the turbines aren't responding.

1685
02:13:03,500 --> 02:13:06,300
跳过这个 手动发动引擎
So override it. Hit the override. Start the engine.

1686
02:13:06,350 --> 02:13:08,600
门没关好就发动不了引擎
We can't start the engine until we close that gate.

1687
02:13:26,820 --> 02:13:29,320
救我 救命啊!
Help me! Help!

1688
02:13:34,200 --> 02:13:38,000
妈妈! 妈妈!
Momma! Momma!

1689
02:13:38,620 --> 02:13:41,500
- 你没事吧? - 我妈咪在那里面 救救她!
- Are you OK? - My mommy is in there. Please help her!

1690
02:13:41,460 --> 02:13:42,790
我们会去救你妈咪的 宝贝
We'll get to your mommy, sweetheart.

1691
02:13:42,830 --> 02:13:44,130
我们会尽全力的 好吗?
They're doing everything they can, okay?

1692
02:13:44,160 --> 02:13:45,300
能和她说话吗?
Can we talk to her?

1693
02:13:45,340 --> 02:13:47,380
我试试看
I'm gonna try to connect us.

1694
02:13:47,420 --> 02:13:48,970
我们要先给他止血!
We have to stop the bleeding!

1695
02:13:49,000 --> 02:13:50,180
用我的皮带
How about my belt?

1696
02:13:50,380 --> 02:13:53,350
柯蒂斯先生? 杰克逊?
Mr. Curtis? Jackson?

1697
02:13:54,680 --> 02:13:56,650
救命! 嘿!
Help! Hey!

1698
02:13:56,680 --> 02:13:58,500
我是艾德里安・赫尔姆斯利 我们在黄石公园见过
It's Adrian Helmsley, we met at Yellowstone.

1699
02:13:58,550 --> 02:14:01,500
太好了 快点把这该死的门打开!
Thats great. Open the God damn door!

1700
02:14:01,600 --> 02:14:03,610
你女儿在我这边!
Your daughter is with me!

1701
02:14:03,650 --> 02:14:06,860
- 莉莉? - 诺亚在哪儿?
- Lilly? - Where's Noah?

1702
02:14:06,900 --> 02:14:08,740
我就在这儿 莉莉
I'm right here, Lil!

1703
02:14:08,770 --> 02:14:10,700
冲击警告!
Impact warning!

1704
02:14:10,740 --> 02:14:14,370
30度以西 45度以东
30°West, 45°East.

1705
02:14:14,410 --> 02:14:18,210
目标高度29035英尺(约8850米)
Target elevation 29,035 feet.

1706
02:14:18,250 --> 02:14:21,500
两万九千英尺? 什么意思?
29,000 feet? What the hell is at 29.000 feet?

1707
02:14:21,540 --> 02:14:25,900
正前方就是珠穆朗玛峰北侧 安海斯先生
We're headed straight for the north face of Mount Everest, Mr. Anheuser.

1708
02:14:26,000 --> 02:14:28,090
如果还不能发动引擎
And if we can't start our engines,

1709
02:14:28,120 --> 02:14:30,170
我们就只能等死了
we will not survive the impact.

1710
02:14:40,350 --> 02:14:43,560
杰克逊 舱门封住了 我们过不去
Jackson, you're sealed off! We can't get to you!

1711
02:14:43,600 --> 02:14:45,450
有东西卡住了液压装置
There's something blocking the hydraulics

1712
02:14:45,480 --> 02:14:48,190
如果不弄出来 我们都死定了
If you can't get it out, none of us are gonna make it

1713
02:14:49,280 --> 02:14:51,700
赫尔姆斯利博士 看这个
Dr. Helmsley, look at this.

1714
02:14:52,320 --> 02:14:53,900
下面全都淹没了
It's completely submerged down there

1715
02:14:53,950 --> 02:14:56,200
根本进不去 无法呼吸
and there's no way for them to get any air.

1716
02:14:56,270 --> 02:14:57,420
没别的办法了!
There is no other way!

1717
02:14:57,450 --> 02:14:59,830
但这是去送死 先生!
But it's a suicide mission, sir!

1718
02:15:07,090 --> 02:15:09,630
我知道卡在哪里 我去试试
I know where it is, I'll give it a try.

1719
02:15:16,050 --> 02:15:18,640
爸爸 等等 我要和你一起去!
Dad, wait, I wanna go with you!

1720
02:15:18,720 --> 02:15:21,120
- 不不不 - 爸爸我想帮你
- No, no, no. - Dad, I wanna help you! No, no, no.

1721
02:15:21,160 --> 02:15:23,520
- 你已经在帮我了 - 爸爸 求你了!
- You are helping me. - Dad, please!

1722
02:15:23,560 --> 02:15:25,400
还记得莉莉出生的时候
Remember when Lilly was born

1723
02:15:25,460 --> 02:15:27,600
你想当她哥哥吗?
and you wanted to be introduced as her big brother?

1724
02:15:28,360 --> 02:15:30,050
她现在很害怕
Well, she's scared now.

1725
02:15:30,080 --> 02:15:31,700
非常需要你
She needs you more than ever.

1726
02:15:31,740 --> 02:15:35,030
如果你安全 我就知道她也安全 明白吗?
If you're safe, I know that she's safe. Do you understand?

1727
02:15:41,540 --> 02:15:43,660
你可以下次再帮我
You can help me out the next time.

1728
02:15:46,540 --> 02:15:48,540
是我们把它卡住了
We caused this thing, it was us.

1729
02:15:48,580 --> 02:15:50,420
我得去搞定它
I gotta go check it out.

1730
02:16:03,640 --> 02:16:05,100
我爱你!
I love you!

1731
02:16:13,360 --> 02:16:16,570
丹增! 他不行了! 他不行了!

1732
02:16:20,660 --> 02:16:22,450
有人能听到我说话吗?
Can you hear me?

1733
02:16:26,360 --> 02:16:27,620
救命!
Help!

1734
02:16:54,530 --> 02:16:55,610
按住!
Press down!

1735
02:16:55,650 --> 02:16:57,490
用手按住!
Press down with your hand!

1736
02:17:05,700 --> 02:17:08,170
一直按住 别松手
Don't stop. Keep pressing!

1737
02:17:24,890 --> 02:17:27,000
不!
No!

1738
02:17:30,310 --> 02:17:35,150
距离撞击1850米
Distance to impact: 1,850 meters

1739
02:17:37,530 --> 02:17:38,700
看见他了
There he is!

1740
02:17:40,280 --> 02:17:41,950
船长 有影像了
Captain! We have a visual!

